Calzada de Don Diego

Calzada de Don Diego is a city in Salamanca, in Spain.

GPS Coordinates of Calzada de Don Diego, Salamanca, Spain

Calzada de Don Diego is located on the latitude of 40.905 and longitude of -5.90279 and has a geohash of ez7b9wt8zh8v.

Cities and Towns near Calzada de Don Diego

The nearest significant population center from Calzada de Don Diego is Canillas de Abajo in Salamanca, Spain, located 2 kilometers or 1 miles ← W of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Provincia de Salamanca (Léon, Spain) located 11 km (7 mi) ↙ SW and Aldehuela de la Bóveda (Salamanca, Spain) located 13 km (8 mi) ↙ SW of Calzada de Don Diego.
